H3.text: What is the state capital of Alabama. Montgomery

A4.text: Montgomery is the capital city of the U.S. state of Alabama.

A5.text: Montgomery is the capital of Alabama, and hosts numerous state government offices, including the office of the Governor, the Alabama Legislature, and the Alabama Supreme Court.
